ygData.messageBody:
>You raise a level! Welcome to level 50!


(I have been trying for a long time to come up with better replies to
"ding!"s than "congrats", "congratz", or "gratz" with little success. "Yay!"
seems too vague, "Bless you!" to ingenuine, "Go to Hell!" too easy to be
taken the wrong way...and "You smell great!" is oddly often misunderstood. I
am stretching out, looking for alternatives, but for the moment I will stick
with the old standby.)

As they say in my guild, "WOOT!", Sylly! (Thats drunken Troll for congrats)
;-P

-Treehugger and Songmaker
Povar
